### No Custom Read Roles Configured

Custom read roles are optional. Use this feature when you need:
- Fine-grained access for external partners
- Restricted access for specific applications
- Compliance-driven access controls

To add custom read roles, update the `custom_read_roles` answer with:
- `name`: Role identifier (e.g., "PARTNER_A")
- `description`: Purpose of the role
- `schema_access`: Comma-separated list of zone.schema (e.g., "GOLD.REPORTING,GOLD.ANALYTICS")

